<article xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
  <section>
    <title> Literal blocks</title>
    <para>Literal blocks may be created just by indentation:</para>
    <literallayout>  Like this.
</literallayout>
    <para>They may be multi-line:</para>
    <literallayout>  Foo.
  Bar
</literallayout>
    <para>Markup is ignored inside:</para>
    <literallayout>  **foo** http://example.org ... [[ / &amp;%/
</literallayout>
    <para>Additional indentation is also ignored:</para>
    <literallayout>  Foo
    Bar
   If you want to preserve indenation, use &lt;code&gt;
  Blubb.
</literallayout>
  </section>
</article>
